<h3>Result of prejudice ?</h3>
<ul>
<li>propagation of stereotypes</li>
<li>tendency of 'othering' different sections of society based on differences.&nbsp;</li>
<li>lack of tolerance</li>
<li>Normalise the violence against 'other' to 'protect self'</li></ul>
<h3>how to counter?&nbsp;</h3>
<ul>
<li>inter group dialogues&nbsp;</li>
<li>individual level and community level ties</li>
<li>inter group blood relations - marriage etc&nbsp;</li>
<li>Concept of multiple identities - creation of 'us' as identity, rather than 'other.'</li>
<li>Open lines of communication.</li></ul>
